-- UniCredit to Name Nicastro Sole General Manager at Meeting, MF Reports
-- B y   J e r r o l d   C o l t e n
-- 2010-10-26T05:24:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-26/unicredit-to-name-nicastro-sole-general-manager-at-meeting-mf-reports.html
UniCredit will name Roberto Nicastro
as its sole general manager at a board meeting today, MF
reported, without saying where it got the information.  The bank will also name Paolo Fiorentino as chief operating
officer, MF said.  UniCredit had been considering naming two general managers,
MF said. Deputy Chief Executive Officer Sergio Ermotti may
decide to leave the company, MF said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jerrold Colten at 
 jcolten@bloomberg.net  